---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const faqSchema = JSON.stringify({
	'@context': 'https://schema.org',
	'@type': 'FAQPage',
	mainEntity: [
		{
			'@type': 'Question',
			name: 'Comment réserver un transfert aéroport à Cancun ?',
			acceptedAnswer: {
				'@type': 'Answer',
				text: 'Contact Elite Ride Mexico via WhatsApp at +52 5644166523 or use our contact form. Share your flight details and we will assign a professional bilingual driver to meet you at Cancun International Airport (CUN).'
			}
		},
		{
			'@type': 'Question',
			name: 'What vehicles are available for Cancun airport transfers?',
			acceptedAnswer: {
				'@type': 'Answer',
				text: 'We offer Chevrolet Suburban, GMC Yukon Denali, Toyota Land Cruiser, and executive vans for private airport transfers in Cancun — ideal for families, corporate groups, and VIP travelers.'
			}
		},
		{
			'@type': 'Question',
			name: 'Is the Cancun airport transfer private or shared?',
			acceptedAnswer: {
				'@type': 'Answer',
				text: 'All our Cancun airport transfers are 100% private. You will not share the vehicle with other passengers. Your driver waits for you at the arrivals hall with a name sign.'
			}
		},
		{
			'@type': 'Question',
			name: 'Do you track my flight for Cancun pickups?',
			acceptedAnswer: {
				'@type': 'Answer',
				text: 'Yes. We monitor your flight status in real time so your driver adjusts arrival time if your flight is delayed, at no extra cost.'
			}
		},
		{
			'@type': 'Question',
			name: 'Which hotels and resorts in Cancun do you serve?',
			acceptedAnswer: {
				'@type': 'Answer',
				text: 'We provide transfers to and from all hotels in the Hotel Zone, downtown Cancun, Playa del Carmen, Tulum, and surrounding areas in the Riviera Maya.'
			}
		}
	]
});

const whatsappLink = 'https://wa.me/525644166523';
---

<Layout
	lang="fr"
	title="Transfert aéroport Cancun | SUV privé et chauffeur | Elite Ride Mexico"
	description="Private airport transfer in Cancun. Meet & greet at CUN, premium SUV, bilingual driver, flight tracking. Hotels, resorts, and Riviera Maya. Book 24/7."
	canonicalURL="https://eliteridemexico.com/fr/cancun-airport-transfer"
  preloadImages={['/contact/cdmx-timeout.webp']}
	alternateHref="https://eliteridemexico.com/cancun-airport-transfer"
	alternateLang="en"
>
	<script type="application/ld+json" slot="head" set:html={faqSchema} />

	<div class="page-wrapper">
		<section>
			<div class="header-section contact-header-section">
				<div class="navbar w-nav">
					<div class="content-wrapper">
						<div class="navbar-wrapper">
							<a href="/" class="brand w-nav-brand">
								<span class="brand-logo-text">ELITE RIDE MEXICO</span>
							</a>
							<nav role="navigation" class="nav-menu-wrapper w-nav-menu">
								<ul role="list" class="nav-menu w-list-unstyled">
									<li class="nav-list-item"><a href="/fr" class="nav-link">Accueil</a></li>
									<li class="nav-list-item"><a href="/fr/about" class="nav-link">A propos</a></li>
									<li class="nav-list-item"><a href="/fr/our-fleet" class="nav-link">Notre flotte</a></li>
									<li class="nav-list-item"><a href="/fr/contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a></li>
									<li class="nav-list-item">
										<div class="cta-button-wrapper">
											<a href="/our-fleet" class="cta-button w-button">réserver</a>
										</div>
									</li>
								</ul>
							</nav>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="content-wrapper">
					<div class="header-section-wrapper">
						<div class="header-content-wrapper">
							<div class="header-text-wrapper contact-header-text-wrapper">
								<h1 class="header-text">Transfert aéroport Cancun — SUV privé et chauffeur</h1>
								<div class="primary-text">
									Transferts privés porte à porte à l aéroport international de Cancun (CUN). SUV premium, chauffeurs bilingues, accueil personnalisé et suivi de vol en temps réel. Disponible 24/7.
								</div>
								<div class="header-button-wrapper">
									<a href={whatsappLink} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="cta-button w-button">
										Réserver sur WhatsApp
									</a>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section bg-white">
			<div class="content-wrapper">
				<h2 class="section-heading">Service de transfert aéroport privé à Cancun</h2>
				<p class="primary-text grey-color" style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto 1.5rem;">
					Arriver à Cancun doit être simple et agréable. Le service de transfert privé Elite Ride Mexico vous accueille à l arrivée avec chauffeur professionnel, aide aux bagages et véhicule premium prêt pour un trajet confortable vers votre destination.
				</p>

				<h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">Ce qui est inclus</h2>
				<div class="grid-wrapper" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">Accueil à CUN</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							Votre chauffeur vous attend dans le hall d arrivée avec une pancarte nominative. Pas d attente, pas de stress.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">Suivi de vol</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							Nous suivons votre vol en temps réel. En cas de retard, votre chauffeur ajuste l horaire sans frais supplémentaires.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">Véhicule 100% privé</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							Aucune navette partagée. Le véhicule est réservé exclusivement pour vous, de l aéroport à votre hôtel ou resort.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">Destinations desservies</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							Hotel Zone, Downtown Cancun, Playa del Carmen, Tulum, Akumal, and all Riviera Maya destinations.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">Véhicules pour transferts aéroport Cancun</h2>
				<p class="primary-text grey-color" style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto 1rem;">
					Service Chevrolet Suburban avec chauffeur, GMC Yukon Denali, Toyota Land Cruiser et vans exécutifs avec climatisation, espace bagages et chauffeur bilingue professionnel.
				</p>
				<div style="text-align:center;margin-top:1.5rem;">
					<a href="/our-fleet" class="cta-button w-button">Voir toute la flotte</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section">
			<div class="content-wrapper">
				<h2 class="section-heading">Questions fréquentes — Cancun Airport Transfer</h2>
				<div class="grid-wrapper" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">Comment réserver un transfert aéroport à Cancun ?</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							Contactez-nous par WhatsApp ou via le formulaire. Envoyez votre numéro de vol, heure d arrivée et hôtel. Confirmation sous 15 à 30 minutes.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">Les transferts sont-ils privés ou partagés ?</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							Tous les transferts sont 100% privés. Vous ne partagez jamais le véhicule avec d autres passagers.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">Suivez-vous mon vol ?</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							Yes. We monitor your flight status so the driver adjusts if there's a delay — at no extra cost.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item-wrapper">
						<div class="title-small">Quelles zones desservez-vous à Cancun ?</div>
						<p class="primary-text grey-color metric-text">
							Hotel Zone, downtown, Playa del Carmen, Tulum, and all Riviera Maya destinations.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section bg-white">
			<div class="content-wrapper" style="text-align:center;">
				<h2 class="section-heading">Book Your Cancun Airport Transfer Now</h2>
				<p class="primary-text grey-color" style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 1.5rem;">
					Available 24/7. Reply within 15 minutes. No hidden fees.
				</p>
				<a href={whatsappLink} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="cta-button w-button">Écrire sur WhatsApp</a>
				<span style="display:inline-block;width:1rem;"></span>
				<a href="/contact" class="cta-button w-button" style="background:#333;">Envoyer une demande</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<div class="footer-section-wrapper">
				<div class="content-wrapper">
					<div class="footer-content-wrapper">
						<div class="footer-top-content">
							<div class="footer-logo-social">
								<a href="/" class="brand w-nav-brand">
									<span class="brand-logo-text footer-brand-logo-text">ELITE RIDE MEXICO</span>
								</a>
								<div class="footer-text">
									Private airport transfers and chauffeur service across Mexico. Premium SUVs, bilingual drivers,
									available 24/7.
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="divider"></div>
						<div class="footer-bottom-content">
							<div class="footer-links-wrapper">
								<h2 class="heading">Pages</h2>
								<a href="/" class="footer-nav-link">Accueil</a>
								<a href="/about" class="footer-nav-link">A propos</a>
								<a href="/our-fleet" class="footer-nav-link">Notre flotte</a>
								<a href="/contact" class="footer-nav-link">Contact</a>
							</div>
							<div class="footer-links-wrapper">
								<h2 class="heading">Services locaux</h2>
								<a href="/mexico-city-private-chauffeur" class="footer-nav-link">Mexico City Chauffeur</a>
								<a href="/cancun-airport-transfer" class="footer-nav-link w--current">Cancun Airport Transfer</a>
								<a href="/guadalajara-private-driver" class="footer-nav-link">Guadalajara Driver</a>
								<a href="/armored-vehicle-rental-mexico" class="footer-nav-link">Véhicules blindés</a>
							</div>
							<div class="footer-links-wrapper">
								<h2 class="heading">Get In Touch</h2>
								<a href="tel:+525644166523" class="footer-nav-link">+52 5644166523</a>
								<a href="mailto:info@eliteridemexico.com" class="footer-nav-link">info@eliteridemexico.com</a>
								<a
									href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Goldsmith+250,+Lomas+de+Chapultepec,+Ciudad+de+Mexico"
									target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="footer-nav-link"
								>Goldsmith 250, Lomas de Chapultepec, Miguel Hidalgo, 11500, CDMX, Mexico</a>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="divider"></div>
						<div class="copyright-info-wrapper">
							<a href="https://www.o7digital.com/en/index-digital-agency" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="footer-copyright-text">
								Copyright Elite Ride Mexico 2026 - made by o7Digital
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<a href={whatsappLink} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="whatsapp-footer-button" aria-label="WhatsApp">
			<img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6677ef5c2f59c6148debf7e0/6677ef5c2f59c6148debf814_whatsapp.png" loading="lazy" alt="WhatsApp Icon" class="whatsapp-footer-icon" />
		</a>
	</div>
</Layout>
